-- CEZ to Save $26 Million Yearly Through Reorganization, Euro Says
-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 2012-11-26T10:23:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-26/cez-to-save-26-million-yearly-through-reorganization-euro-says.html
CEZ AS (CEZ)  will save as much as 500
million koruna ($26 million) a year by reducing headcount and
merging several of its back-office companies, Euro reported,
citing Strategy Director Pavel Cyrani.  To contact the reporter on this story:
